                             throws ExceptionClass extends ApplicationException.Error
        Moves this node within the tree using absolutePath as the absolute navigator. Last node will be treated as the new node name e.g.: subnode/newname = /parent/thisnode -> /subnode/newname parent/subnode/thisnode = /parent/thisnode -> /parent/subnode/thisnode
